<pre>Createch strives to transform the traditional academic instruction to an environment that combines innovative technology and creativity. The club aspires to enrich the intellectual as well as the cultural life of the campus. \r\nEach year the club organizes the much awaited two-day annual technical fest of the university - \'Murious\'\r\nMurious aims at bringing out talent in students from all domains to vie for honor. With events ranging from robotics to programming to some fun-and-frolic events like junkyard wars, it tries to give JUITian’s a respite from their routine toil.\r\nThe members of this club come together each year to organize these events for the biggest annual festival of this university and work together towards the successful execution of the events. Our goal is to bring a chance to explore the intellect, agility and creativity of the students of JUIT.</pre>